biography:
Jacob Daniel Tierney (born September 26, 1979) is a Canadian actor, film director and screenwriter.

Tierney was born in Montreal, Quebec, the son of veteran producer Kevin Tierney. He starred in the 1993 film Josh and S.A.M.
